            'bio' => 'Michael Rogers was born on May 18, 1964 in Victoria, British Columbia, Canada as Michael John Rogers. He is an actor and writer, known for The Assassination of Jesse James by the Coward Robert Ford (2007), Beyond the Black Rainbow (2010) and Duets (2000).',
